it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface JumpExtCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Command, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface JumpExtCommand
extends Command
    A representation of the model object 'Jump Ext Command'. Permette di far passare il flusso di esecuzione ad una pagina esterna all'applicativo.

    The following features are supported:

    • Static Url
    • Runtime Url Provider
    • Location Code
    • Binary Stream
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getJumpExtCommand()
